And I said to them look I have
to tell you I make my money

00:51:54.370 --> 00:51:58.240
through licensing images and
through creating photography

00:51:58.240 --> 00:52:01.790
and quite frankly I'm not an
architectural photographer.

00:52:01.790 --> 00:52:05.020
I did these images of the bridge
just because it was something

00:52:05.020 --> 00:52:08.400
that I happened to like,
